            "text": "Minor follow-up on Zulip. Mainly of interest to <@UC2A2ARPT>. I've been missing Zulip's channel view for a couple of months now. Turns out they put it into the context menu. And you get out of it if you breathe on the thing wrong. They basically took the essence of Zulip and completely fucked it up. If I wanted per-topic views I could go use, like, phpBB.\n\nThere is no way around it. People that talk together should run their own platform and potentially write their own platform. The medium is the message.",
